Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.48,0:00:04.38,Housei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,326.073)}You know how I am really talented with music?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.08,0:00:06.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,2 years ago, he made original\Nsongs for the Gaki members
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.58,0:00:08.02,Housei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,368.704)} I made you all songs...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.38,0:00:11.32,WhiteTextS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(497.804,124.709)}Narrator:\NNoda Keiichi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.92,0:00:10.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,to try and live off royalties\Nfor the rest of his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.02,0:00:10.39,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(271.948,369.23)}Am I actually going to sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.99,0:00:10.39,Housei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(496.369,369.231)}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.39,0:00:12.06,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,368.704)}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.19,0:00:13.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We were all shocked by his talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.23,0:00:14.03,Housei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,368.704)}To sell...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.26,0:00:18.00,RomajiKara,,0,0,0,,{\pos(317.759,426.588)}♫ Machi no man'naka de haretsusuru ♫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.26,0:00:18.00,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It explodes in the middle of the town
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.00,0:00:21.67,RomajiKara,,0,0,0,,{\pos(317.759,426.588)}♫ Osae kirenai yokubō to ♫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.00,0:00:21.67,Hamada,,0,0,0,,The desire that I cannot suppress anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.67,0:00:24.14,RomajiKara,,0,0,0,,{\pos(317.759,426.588)}♫ Mou ♫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.67,0:00:24.14,Matsu,,0,0,0,,It seems
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.14,0:00:27.81,RomajiKara,,0,0,0,,{\pos(317.759,426.588)}♫ Modorenai ♫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.14,0:00:27.81,Matsu,,0,0,0,,That we've come
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.81,0:00:32.68,RomajiKara,,0,0,0,,{\pos(317.759,426.588)}♫ Tokoro made kita mitaida ♫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.81,0:00:32.68,Matsu,,0,0,0,,To a point where we can't return anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.51,0:00:32.68,HamadaC,,0,0,0,,The theme of this song makes you look so lame...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:36.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,However, no one from\Nthe music industry called...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:40.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So tonight, in order to save\Nhis reputation, Yamasaki will try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.52,0:00:40.89,GreenT,,0,0,0,,{\pos(232.578,36.072)}Yamasaki Produce
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.42,0:00:44.06,Housei,,0,0,0,,It's been 2 years since the last one,\Nthis is the 2nd installment of Yamasaki Produce.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.49,0:00:44.06,BlueO,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(317.359,378.23)}Yamasaki Housei
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.06,0:00:46.06,GreenO,,0,0,0,,{\pos(134.654,362.388)}Downtown
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.06,0:00:46.06,BlueO,,0,0,0,,{\pos(149.967,417.651)}Matsumoto\NHitoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.06,0:00:46.06,BlueO,,0,0,0,,{\pos(289.901,229.757)}Cocorico
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.06,0:00:46.06,BlueO,,0,0,0,,{\pos(340.594,269.23)}Endo Shozo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.06,0:00:46.06,Matsu,,0,0,0,,I totally forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.06,0:00:46.06,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's been that long?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.06,0:00:49.59,Housei,,0,0,0,,We've all done the filming\Nthis time already, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.69,0:00:49.59,Endo,,0,0,0,,Yes we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.59,0:00:51.60,Matsu,,0,0,0,,I am just done...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.60,0:00:53.60,Housei,,0,0,0,,But seriously,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.60,0:00:55.43,Housei,,0,0,0,,we've actually done three songs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.90,0:00:57.14,GreenO,,0,0,0,,{\pos(494.258,326.073)}Downtown
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.90,0:00:57.14,BlueO,,0,0,0,,{\pos(508.516,382.915)}Hamada\NMasatoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.43,0:00:57.34,Housei,,0,0,0,,this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.57,0:00:58.30,Endo,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:00:58.94,Housei,,0,0,0,,A solo for Endo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:00:59.67,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(322.112,407.125)}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.94,0:01:01.31,Housei,,0,0,0,,Then a duet for\NMatsumoto-san and Tanaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:04.11,Matsu,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what the hell was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:04.11,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Wow awesome, that'll be incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:04.58,BlueO,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\pos(321.583,401.862)}Tanaka Naoki
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:04.58,BlueO,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\pos(269.306,376.598)}Cocorico
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.11,0:01:06.78,Housei,,0,0,0,,And lastly, all 5 of us,\Nwith Hamada-san being the main lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.78,0:01:08.31,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Well, we did it together...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.21,0:01:15.05,YellowT,,0,0,0,,{\pos(331.089,318.177)}Yamasaki made the song and lyrics
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.31,0:01:11.55,Housei,,0,0,0,,And they're all really good songs this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:13.45,Housei,,0,0,0,,Last time, unfortunately...{\alphaFF}\Nnone of them became CDs
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.45,0:01:15.05,Housei,,0,0,0,,Last time, unfortunately...\Nnone of them became CDs
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:18.06,Matsu,,0,0,0,,You say unfortunately but we had no plans to make it into a CD anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.06,0:01:21.19,Housei,,0,0,0,,No, but seriously Matsumoto-san,\Nyour song last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.19,0:01:22.99,Housei,,0,0,0,,was good--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.19,0:01:22.99,RomajiKara,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320.927,397.016)}♫ Mou ♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.19,0:01:22.99,Matsu,,0,0,0,,It seems...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.99,0:01:25.86,RomajiKara,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320.927,428.595)}♫ Modorenai ♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.99,0:01:25.86,All,,0,0,0,,That we've come
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.86,0:01:28.87,RomajiKara,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320.927,428.595)}♫ Tokoro made-- ♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.86,0:01:28.87,Housei,,0,0,0,,To a point--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.30,0:01:28.87,Matsu,,0,0,0,,You're going to continue singing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.87,0:01:32.47,Matsu,,0,0,0,,There was a bit of a laugh\Nfrom the staff so just leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.47,0:01:36.51,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Man, that's lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.14,0:01:36.51,Housei,,0,0,0,,It really is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.51,0:01:41.98,RomajiKara,,0,0,0,,♫ Bokura no te ni wa todokanai ♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.98,0:01:44.75,Housei,,0,0,0,,The music this time is also awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.15,0:01:46.65,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:46.65,Housei,,0,0,0,,First up, Endo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.65,0:01:49.75,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,It's a solo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.65,0:01:49.75,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Endo up first.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:49.75,Matsu,,0,0,0,,Oh this one, I've not
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.75,0:01:53.02,Matsu,,0,0,0,,got a clue about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.89,0:01:52.42,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:54.59,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,This will be the first time we see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.02,0:01:55.43,Matsu,,0,0,0,,So I'm looking forward to seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.73,0:02:12.51,RehearsalT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(40.296,52.02)}During Rehearsal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.86,0:02:00.30,Housei,,0,0,0,,When I think of your song,\Nmy creativity just goes crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:02.63,Endo,,0,0,0,,Oh, well I'm very thankful to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:02.63,Housei,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.63,0:02:05.34,Housei,,0,0,0,,So, can you listen to this once?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.34,0:02:07.71,Endo,,0,0,0,,Um... wait, just before that,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.71,0:02:10.98,Endo,,0,0,0,,last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:12.91,Endo,,0,0,0,,it was death metal right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:12.91,Housei,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.31,0:02:17.52,TanakaC,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.52,0:02:20.39,EndoC,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:23.05,Housei,,0,0,0,,Last time,{\alphaFF} you were awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.05,0:02:24.99,Housei,,0,0,0,,Last time, you were awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.22,0:02:26.29,Endo,,0,0,0,,Yeah, honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:27.66,Housei,,0,0,0,,You were like the Endo who I hate the most...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:29.49,Housei,,0,0,0,,I hate that kind of Endo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.49,0:02:31.06,Housei,,0,0,0,,So this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.06,0:02:33.03,Housei,,0,0,0,,it's totally different, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:34.13,Endo,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.03,0:02:36.23,Housei,,0,0,0,,I want you to sing this seriously
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.23,0:02:40.14,Housei,,0,0,0,,and to hear your beautiful voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:40.14,Endo,,0,0,0,,Ah, OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:42.41,Housei,,0,0,0,,So let's take a listen first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.35,0:03:00.93,RomajiKara,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,427.98)}♫ Wasurerarenai Summer ♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.35,0:03:00.93,Housei,,0,0,0,,That unforgettable Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.29,0:02:59.56,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(321.585,395.546)}It's actually Japanese this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.56,0:03:00.76,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(378.615,395.545)}Like properly...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.56,0:03:00.76,Housei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(221.783,397.124)}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.73,0:03:05.23,Endo,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.10,0:03:15.71,RomajiKara,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,399.56)}♫ Enoshima no umi ja wakareta onna ga hitori ♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.10,0:03:15.71,Housei,,0,0,0,, There was a girl who had just split up,\Nalone at Enoshima, by the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:19.01,RomajiKara,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,427.98)}♫ Namida misezu ni ♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:19.01,Housei,,0,0,0,,Without showing tears
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:22.38,Housei,,0,0,0,,So listen and make sure you understand
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:23.85,Housei,,0,0,0,,it's about summer--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:25.45,Endo,,0,0,0,,Wait a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:28.22,Endo,,0,0,0,,It's a medley?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:29.45,Housei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(313.663,393.967)}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:30.82,Endo,,0,0,0,,But I've only just listened to\Nthis song for the first time ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:33.66,Endo,,0,0,0,,and I have to do a medley suddenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:33.66,Housei,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.66,0:03:35.33,Housei,,0,0,0,,In my head
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.33,0:03:38.23,Housei,,0,0,0,,you've already released loads of hit songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:39.83,Endo,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.83,0:03:42.23,Endo,,0,0,0,,I don't get the meaning of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.23,0:03:45.54,Housei,,0,0,0,,Seriously, in my head I just\Nstarted imagining loads of things
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:47.87,Housei,,0,0,0,,and I got loads of good ideas for songs.
