Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.51,0:12:10.68,Hamada,,0,0,0,,And you had to do that dance the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:10.68,Matsu,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.68,0:12:14.15,Matsu,,0,0,0,,I thought whilst doing it,\N"Someone has done this kind of dance before."
