Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.03,0:12:40.04,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,and then,\NMatsumoto falls in love with Chiaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:41.04,Matsu,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:44.64,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,So he falls in love, and this isn't a song\Nbetween Endo and Matsumoto as rivals
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:46.64,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,it's a song about me and Matsumoto-san
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:49.28,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,where I am supporting him to win...
