Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:13:00.36,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and it becomes complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:13:00.36,Matsu,,0,0,0,,There's no reason to\Ninclude him anyway, but...
